extends layout

block content
  // Page Header
  .page-header.row.no-gutters.py-4
    .col-12.col-sm-4.text-center.text-sm-left.mb-0
      span.text-uppercase.page-subtitle Overview
      h3.page-title User Profile
  // End Page Header
  // Default Light Table
  .row
    .col-lg-4
      .card.card-small.mb-4.pt-3
        .card-header.border-bottom.text-center
          .mb-3.mx-auto
            img.rounded-circle(src='images/avatars/0.jpg' alt='User Avatar' width='110')
          // <img class="rounded-circle" src="images/avatars/0.jpg" alt="User Avatar" width="110"> </div>
          h4.mb-0 Arnold Schwarz
          span.text-muted.d-block.mb-2 Front End Developer
          button.mb-2.btn.btn-sm.btn-pill.btn-outline-primary.mr-2(type='button')
            i.material-icons.mr-1 person_add
            | Follow
        ul.list-group.list-group-flush
          li.list-group-item.px-4
            .progress-wrapper
              strong.text-muted.d-block.mb-2 Workload
              .progress.progress-sm
                .progress-bar.bg-primary(role='progressbar' aria-valuenow='74' aria-valuemin='0' aria-valuemax='100' style='width: 74%;')
                  span.progress-value 74%
          li.list-group-item.p-4
            strong.text-muted.d-block.mb-2 Description
            span
              | Alright everyone and if you do not listen, the hell with you, but i&apos;m all woman. c-coo-ool. Danger&apos;s my trade. Doesn&apos;t anyone stay dead anymore? Don&apos;t disturb my friend. Here, I have my orders. It&apos;s all bull. Get your ass to Mars.
    .col-lg-8
      .card.card-small.mb-4
        .card-header.border-bottom
          h6.m-0 Account Details
        ul.list-group.list-group-flush
          li.list-group-item.p-3
            .row
              .col
                form
                  .form-row
                    .form-group.col-md-6
                      label(for='feFirstName') First Name
                      input#feFirstName.form-control(type='text' placeholder='First Name' value='Arnold')
                    .form-group.col-md-6
                      label(for='feLastName') Last Name
                      input#feLastName.form-control(type='text' placeholder='Last Name' value='Schwarz')
                  .form-row
                    .form-group.col-md-6
                      label(for='feEmailAddress') Email
                      input#feEmailAddress.form-control(type='email' placeholder='Email' value='arnold@aol.com')
                    .form-group.col-md-6
                      label(for='fePassword') Password
                      input#fePassword.form-control(type='password' placeholder='Password')
                  .form-group
                    label(for='feInputAddress') Address
                    input#feInputAddress.form-control(type='text' placeholder='1234 Main St')
                  .form-row
                    .form-group.col-md-6
                      label(for='feInputCity') City
                      input#feInputCity.form-control(type='text')
                    .form-group.col-md-4
                      label(for='feInputState') State
                      select#feInputState.form-control
                        option(selected='') Choose...
                        option ...
                    .form-group.col-md-2
                      label(for='inputZip') Zip
                      input#inputZip.form-control(type='text')
                  .form-row
                    .form-group.col-md-12
                      label(for='feDescription') Description
                      textarea.form-control(name='feDescription' rows='5')
                        | Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Odio eaque, quidem, commodi soluta qui quae minima obcaecati quod dolorum sint alias, possimus illum assumenda eligendi cumque?
                  button.btn.btn-accent(type='submit') Update Account
  // End Default Light Table
